            <description><![CDATA[【惊险！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%95%E5%80%92AED%E5%8F%88%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%91%BD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%95%E5%80%92AED%E5%8F%88%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%91%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳地铁一男子晕倒AED又救人一命#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_xin-43af9086c0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】近日，在深圳地铁4号线上，一名年轻男子突然晕倒，无自主呼吸，情况危急！周围一名乘客立即联系地铁工作人员，另一名乘客拨打120急救。列车到站后，站长立刻进行心肺复苏，并使用AED除颤，将乘客从“死神”手里拽回！随后乘客被送往医院治疗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[中国赞]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_chnlike-8fc550a807.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳地铁上一男子晕倒多人齐心救援#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4983494980337689" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">第一现场的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6aac5feagy1hl83m3vosnj20u01hc76u.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/4yK8UpdQgx08bgwND6Qw01041200edfH0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720